						               													<description>Candy and Cola is a single miniature expansion for Super Dungeon Explore. It was provided with some copies of the game as well as a separate purchase.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Candy and Cola has the following abilities:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Luck: Can select between potions and hearts, as known from the Riftling Rogue.&amp;#10; - Cola: Rolls a blue dice in each activation and gains potions according to the number of stars.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;They also have the following special action:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Vending Machine: For 2 actions they can remove a potion and place it on another hero (range 6).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Finally, they can spend potions:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Soothing Soda (1 potion): Immune to status effects.&amp;#10; - Sugar Rush (3 potions): +2 actions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is worth noting that Candy and Cola can carry 3 potions!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
